Why this is better
	•	Single pass over the deltas; no repeated JSON tree walks.
	•	Handles both CREATE (no deltas) and MODIFY (deltas present).
	•	Fully stateless & thread‑safe (no shared mutable state).
	•	Works with your existing ChangeInfo class and tracked‑fields pipeline.

